  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    CantPerformActionException
    This exception is thrown when you cant perform an action. The superclass for exception NotEnoughActionPointsException and exception NotEnoughManaPointsException.
    ClientNetworkException
    This exception is thrown when the client gets wrong input from the server
    GameEnded
    This exception is thrown when the game is ended
    NotEnoughActionPointsException
    This exception is thrown when you dont have enough action points to do something.
    NotEnoughManaPointsException
    This exception is thrown when you dont have enough mana points to do something.
